/**
create_dbtest80.py - automates installation of DBTEST80 productline
run_test.py - automates setup and running of Java regression tests on DBTEST80 productline
**/

/**Step-by-step setup**/

1. Download and install Python in your machine. Python 3 is preferred but this will also run in Python 2 (I think ;) ).
2. Create database instance for DBTEST80 productline
3. Edit dbtest80.cfg and provide all the necessary entries for creating the database capfile and editda file
4. Run init.bat/enter.cmd depending on whether you're using a binary box or a sandbox
5. CD to the location of the Python scripts
6. Run python create_dbtest80.py
7. Run python run_test.py